cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as segmentation and proposes a method for transferring knowledge from virtual to real-world scenes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering, which suggests the possibility of cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The proposed method involves deep learning and GANs, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions the application of the proposed method to robotics, which could relate to cs.RO (Robotics).
